We may collect the following information when you use our app:
We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, or other details you provide voluntarily. We may also collect usage data, including pages visited, time spent in the app, clicks, and other analytics. If you allow location access, we may collect your location information to provide trip suggestions. Additionally, we may collect device information such as your device type, operating system, and app version.

We use your information to provide trip planning services, improve app performance and features, personalize recommendations, and send you updates and notifications.

We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information only with service providers, such as Firebase or analytics tools, to operate the app, when required by law, or to protect the safety and security of our users.

TripVisor uses third-party tools like Google Firebase for authentication, database, and analytics, and Google AdMob to display ads. These services may collect information as per their own privacy policies.

We use industry-standard measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

You can disable location access in your device settings. You can also request data deletion by contacting us at [your support email].

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of changes by posting the updated policy in the app.

